\par\pard\plain \tx0\li360\fi360\sa120\ltrch\loch {\f4\fs22\b0\i0\cf6 In previous scenes, Laura and Evan masterminded a scholarship scheme, acting as co-conspirators to covertly and deceitfully award a scholarship to Maggie. In the scene prior, they executed the final step before Maggie is to be informed she's the recipient of the scholarship. The current scene unfolds with Laura returning to the apartment after checking the mail. Unknown to Maggie at this moment is that Laura slipped in the envelope containing her $15,000 check and a congratulatory letter. Evan arrives with Laura, passing off their simultaneous return as mere coincidence.<!$Scr_Ps::2>}
